-- PVP summary:      +-+------- breaking API changes
--                   | | +----- non-breaking API additions
--                   | | | +--- code changes with no API change
version:             0.1.0.0

-- A short (one-line) description of the package.
synopsis: A poorly written interface to the d3 library from Haste.

-- A longer description of the package.
description: This is a misguided attempt at making a library for using the d3 javascript library in Haste.  This package is called haste-d2 so that a better, more well thought out library can one day use the name haste-d3 without this garbage blocking things.  The author has delusions of grandeur that he might one day be competent enough to write that library, but don't hold your breath.

